name: Southwest Airlines Full Flight | Dallas to Lubbock, TX | Boeing 737-500
description:
A full length, full flight video from Dallas Love Field to Lubbock, TX with Southwest Airlines onboard Boeing 737-500 N520SW operating flight WN22 on August 14 2016.

This full flight video kindly submitted by CessnaN64107 - check out his awesome channel at https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmWKnbmkFq8TZyxJbFj28GA :)

If you would like to share your own full flight videos on inflight Video then please send me a message!

**Every moment of the flight included from gate to gate**

PLEASE SUBSCRIBE FOR WEEKLY FULL FLIGHTSFACEBOOK: facebook.com/inflightvideo

INSTAGRAM: instagram.com/inflightvideo

Airline:  Southwest Airlines
Flight:  WN22
Aircraft:  Boeing 737-500 N520SW
From:  Dallas Love Field (DAL)
To:  Lubbock, TX (LBB)
Departure:  13:15
Arrival:  14:00
Flight Time:  0:45
Seat:  16F
Flight Path: https://goo.gl/injvKP

Our flight today begins on stand at Dallas' Love Field Airport.  Once boarding is complete we push back and taxi to the runway, ahead of a 50 minute flight to the remote airport at Lubbock, TX.  After a smooth flight we enter a bumpy descent into Lubbock, landing on runway 08.

Filmed from seat 16F
